# Treelogic Medical Image De-identification System

## Abstract

This project presents a comprehensive system for medical image de-identification that complies with AI Act (EU), GDPR, and HIPAA regulations. Developed for the Treelogic Visual De-identification Challenge, the system implements an end-to-end pipeline that detects text using OCR, automatically classifies Protected Health Information (PHI), and anonymizes images while preserving clinical utility.

**Key Features:** SSIM threshold of 0.99 or higher, zero modification of healthy tissue, complete fulfillment of all 21 hackathon requirements.

