## Key Features

### Regulatory Compliance
- **AI Act (EU):** SSIM threshold of 0.99 or higher with bit-level validation
- **GDPR:** Irreversible anonymization with Privacy by Design principles
- **HIPAA:** Local processing architecture (Zero-Trust Edge)

### Modern Interface
- React 19 with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS
- Treelogic corporate branding
- Real-time visual feedback

### Scientific Metrics
- SSIM (Structural Similarity Index)
- PSNR (Peak Signal-to-Noise Ratio)
- Bit-level validation (healthy_changed_pixels = 0)

### Zero-Trust Architecture
- 100% local processing
- Data never leaves the device
- No cloud dependencies, API keys, or tracking

### Production Monitoring
- Prometheus metrics endpoint
- Structured JSON logging
- Advanced health checks with system metrics
- 20+ automated monitoring tests

