## Technical Architecture

### Technology Stack

**Backend:**
- FastAPI framework with Python 3.12+
- EasyOCR with GPU support
- OpenCV and scikit-image for image processing
- Port: 8000

**Frontend:**
- React 19 with TypeScript
- Vite 7 build tool with Tailwind CSS 4
- Port: 3000

### Project Structure

```
project/
├── client/                      # React frontend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── pages/              # Application pages
│   │   ├── components/         # UI components
│   │   └── lib/                # Utility functions
│   └── public/
│       └── treelogic-logo.svg
├── server/                      # Python backend
│   ├── main.py                 # FastAPI application
│   ├── monitoring.py           # Observability module
│   ├── text_locator.py         # PHI detection
│   ├── medical_inpainter.py    # Anonymization
│   └── pipeline_validator.py   # Validation
├── tests/                       # Test suite
│   ├── test_monitoring.py      # Monitoring tests (20 tests)
│   ├── test_text_locator.py    # PHI detection tests (32 tests)
│   ├── test_medical_inpainter.py # Inpainting tests (25 tests)
│   └── test_pipeline_validator.py # Pipeline tests (18 tests)
├── docs/                        # Documentation
│   ├── hackathon/              # Compliance, presentation, pitch
│   ├── technical/              # Code analysis, implementation details
│   └── project/                # Branding, issues, metrics
└── shared/                      # Shared TypeScript types
```

